circumstances, concurred to distort, making higher than true, the incidence of 
cancer in M.N.G. We conclude that M.N.G. cannot be considered as a condition 
predisposing to cancer but it may harbour a cancer; since that selective 
surgical approach is recommenced. Selection criteria for surgery and treatment 
are mentioned.

